<section class="page-hero page-hero--short">
  <div class="page-hero-bg">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503220317375-aaad61436b1b?w=1400&q=80" alt="About" />
    <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</p>
    <h1>About Wanderlust</h1>
    <p>Born from a belief that travel, done right, changes who you are.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <div class="about-intro-text">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Since 2007</p>
        <h2>We Are Not a Travel Agency.<br/><em>We Are Architects of Experience.</em></h2>
        <p>Wanderlust was founded in 2007 by two friends who had grown frustrated with travel that felt pre-packaged and impersonal — holidays that checked boxes without touching the soul. They believed the world deserved to be experienced differently: with depth, with intention, and with genuine wonder.</p>
        <p>Today, our team of 40 specialist curators spans six continents. Each curator lives in — and deeply loves — the regions they design for. We don't read guidebooks. We write them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-intro-img">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?w=600&q=80" alt="Our team" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-bar stats-bar--inline">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">{{stats.destinations}}</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Destinations Curated</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">{{stats.travelers}}+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Travelers Transformed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">{{stats.years}}</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years of Excellence</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <span class="stat-num">{{stats.awards}}</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Industry Awards</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="values-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">What We Believe</p>
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">◈</div>
          <h3>Depth Over Breadth</h3>
          <p>We would rather give you three extraordinary days in one place than rush you through ten. Knowing a place means sitting with it, feeling its rhythm, earning its secrets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">◉</div>
          <h3>Authentic Connection</h3>
          <p>We connect travelers with local families, artisans, chefs, and storytellers — not performance culture. The dinner in a stranger's kitchen will outlast any Michelin star.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">◎</div>
          <h3>Responsible Wandering</h3>
          <p>Every itinerary we craft considers environmental impact. We partner with operators who protect ecosystems, compensate communities fairly, and practice conservation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">⬡</div>
          <h3>Obsessive Detail</h3>
          <p>The thread count of your sheets, the 6am light at a particular temple, the cheese made three villages over — these details are why our travelers come back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493246507139-91e8fad9978e?w=1400&q=80" alt="Mountains" />
    <div class="cta-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="cta-content">
    <h2>Ready to Travel Differently?</h2>
    <p>Let's build something unforgettable together.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Start the Conversation</a>
  </div>
</section>
